message: Fannie Pierce says "Just know if someone comes up to your child and says do you want to make extra money that's an indicator that person coming up to them may be recruiting them for tracking."

data.description: A billion dollar industry that many don't know exist is closer than you may think. Human Trafficking is an industry growing day by day and changing lives forever that affects all ages and genders.
data.title: Human Trafficking is a billion dollar industry that is taking over the U.S
